#COVID19: Kwara has emerged the top state in #COVID19 #vaccine preparation and implementation in the country.
Kwara currently leads with 61% while Benue and Bauchi follows with 51% vaccination proportion according to NPHD.
Kudos to Gov @RealAARahman for his sterling work.
